comments: Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the North Hertfordshire unparished area.
Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Wymondley.

Abolished 1894 and divided into the parishes of Hitchin Urban, 
    Walsworth, Preston and Langley.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Hitchin in Hitchin 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the North Hertfordshire 
    unparished area.

Transferred from Bedfordshire to Hertfordshire on 30.9.1897. See 
    also Table 2, notes (b) and (q).

The part in Bedfordshire  was transferred to Hertfordshire on 
    20.10.1844. See also Table 2, notes (b), (h), (i), (l), (m) and (q).

Created 1894 out of the parish of Hitchin. See also Table 2, note 
    (q).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the North Hertfordshire unparished area. See also Table 
    2, note (n).
Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Wymondley.

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parishes of Baldock, 
    Hitchin Urban and Letchworth. See also Table 2, note (q).
Abolished 1.4.1908 and added to the parish of Letchworth.

Created 1894 out of the parish of Hitchin. See also Table 2, note 
    (q).

Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Stevenage unparished area. See 
    also Table 2, note (q).
See Table 2, notes (j), (k), (p) and (q). Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Stevenage unparished area.

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parishes 
    of Shephall and Stevenage and the parts of the parishes of Aston and 
    Datchworth. See also Table 2, notes (o) and (p).

Created 1894 out of the parish of Hitchin. Abolished 1.4.1921 
    and added to the parish of Hitchin Urban.
Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Letchworth.

Created 1.4.1937 out of the parishes of Great Wymondley, Little 
    Wymondley and Ippollits. See also Table 2, note (p).
